3Cli%3EFrom%20prompting%20and%20debugging%20to%20filming%20the%20demo%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20how%20it%20all%20unfolded.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20sunrise%2C%20four%20vibe%20coding%20enthusiasts%20from%20Malaysia%20crossed%20into%20Singapore%20with%20a%20loose%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20bet%20that%20AI%20could%20build%20most%20of%20their%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20they%20were%20racing%20to%20prototype%20it%20at%20Google's%20Gemini%203%20Hackathon%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20friends%2C%20all%20in%20their%20late%2030s%20to%2040s%2C%20came%20from%20different%20professional%20backgrounds.%20Chan%20Wei%20Khjan%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccountant-how-to-learn-vibe-coding-ai-tools-workshop-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20accountant%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Chan%20Ler-Kuan%20lectures%20on%20AI%20at%20a%20private%20university.%20Loh%20Wah%20Kiang%20works%20in%20IT.%20Lee%20How%20Siem%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20Benny%2C%20is%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20a%20Malaysian%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20initial%20idea%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfeng%20shui%26quot%3B%20app%20to%20analyze%20properties%20in%20Singapore%20%E2%80%94%20a%20potentially%20lucrative%20use%20case%20in%20a%20market%20obsessed%20with%20housing%20and%20wealth%20accumulation.%20Feng%20shui%20is%20a%20traditional%20Chinese%20practice%20that%20evaluates%20how%20a%20person's%20surroundings%2C%20along%20with%20birth%20factors%2C%20influence%20luck%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20embedded%20with%20the%20team%20at%20Google's%20developer%20space%20in%20Singapore%20in%20January%20to%20observe%20how%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-on-vibe-coding-ai-tools-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe-coding%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20together%20%E2%80%94%20or%20nearly%20falls%20apart%20%E2%80%94%20in%20seven%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E9%3A30%20a.m.%3A%20The%20brief%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gemini%203%20hackathon%20brief%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696eebbea645d1188187989f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20Chong%20Ming%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assignment%3A%20Teams%20of%20up%20to%20four%20people%20had%20to%20build%20a%20working%20demo%2C%20publish%20a%20public%20repository%20with%20code%2C%20and%20submit%20a%20short%20video%20explaining%20their%20project%20by%205%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20project%20had%20to%20fit%20into%20one%20of%20six%20tracks%2C%20including%20generative%20media%2C%20deep%20research%2C%20and%20enterprise%20orchestration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrganized%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20DeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2065labs%2C%20Singapore's%20AI%20builder%20collective%2C%20the%20hackathon%20featured%20a%20100%2C000-credit%20Gemini%20API%20prize%20pool%2C%20with%20first%20place%20getting%2030%2C000%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20189%20participants%20had%20built%2076%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E10%3A30%20a.m.%3A%20Getting%20started%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hackathon%20team%20getting%20started%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696eec24a645d118818798a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20Chong%20Ming%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20had%20pivoted%20to%20a%20new%20idea%20due%20to%20time%20constraints%3A%20a%20feng%20shui%20app%20that%20could%20analyse%20a%20user's%20outfit%20and%20workspace%20through%20the%20phone%20camera%20in%20real%20time%20and%20assess%20how%20%26quot%3Blucky%26quot%3B%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%