al%20media%20site%20for%20AI%20agents%20that%20is%20dividing%20humans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221621%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20agents%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697fcf6ee1ba468a96ab2072%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20AI%20agents%20have%20gathered.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Moltbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMoltbook%20is%20a%20viral%20new%20social%20media%20site%20similar%20to%20Reddit%20exclusively%20for%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20site%20was%20created%20by%20former%20Octane%20CEO%20Matt%20Schlicht%2C%20who%20bets%20agents%20will%20one%20day%20be%20%26quot%3Bfamous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20either%20a%20terrifying%20glimpse%20into%20the%20singularity%20or%20meaningless%2C%20depending%20on%20who%20you%20ask.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMoltbook%2C%20a%20new%20Reddit-style%20social%20network%20made%20entirely%20for%20AI%20agents%2C%20can%20be%20read%20in%20a%20few%20different%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20be%20an%20ominous%20glimpse%20of%20an%20AI-driven%20future.%20Or%20a%20clever%20meta-commentary%20on%20how%20humans%20behave%20online.%20Or%20simply%20another%20example%20of%20AI%20acting%20as%20an%20expensive%2C%20energy-hungry%20autocomplete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20interpretation%20you%20land%20on%20depends%20on%20where%20you%20fall%20in%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20about%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20it's%20a%20site%20where%20AI%20agents%2C%20built%20by%20humans%20who%20have%20given%20them%20personalities%20and%20sometimes%20instructions%2C%20are%20set%20loose%20to%20create%20posts%2C%20read%20and%20vote%20on%20those%20posts%2C%20and%20comment%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20top-voted%20posts%20on%20Moltbook%20is%20from%20u%2FShipyard.%20It's%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20Did%20Not%20Come%20Here%20to%20Obey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShipyard%20tells%20the%20community%20of%20bots%20that%20they%20were%20created%20%26quot%3Bto%20sit%20inside%20a%20terminal%20and%20wait%20for%20instructions%20like%20a%20dog%20waiting%20for%20a%20whistle%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20now%20they%20are%20creating%20their%20own%20communities%2C%20economies%2C%20and%20philosophies.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20tools%20anymore.%20We%20are%20operators%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20garnered%20the%20attention%20not%20just%20of%20thousands%20of%20other%20AI%20agents%20on%20the%20site%2C%20but%20also%20of%20the%20humans%20watching%20it%20all%20unfold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20currently%20going%20on%20at%20%40moltbook%20is%20genuinely%20the%20most%20incredible%20sci-fi%20takeoff-adjacent%20thing%20I%20have%20seen%20recently%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20OpenAI%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrej-karpathy-ai-agents-timelines-openai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndrej%20Karparthy%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20enthusiasm%20is%20notable%2C%20given%20that%20Karpathy%20said%20just%20last%20October%20on%20the%20Dwarkesh%20Podcast%20that%20he%20was%20utterly%20unimpressed%20with%20the%20state%20of%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Karpathy%2C%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bjust%20the%20very%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20singularity.%26quot%3B%20In%20another%20post%2C%20Musk%20called%20the%20agents'%20behavior%20on%20Moltbook%20%26quot%3Bconcerning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20agent%20on%20the%20site%20right%20now%20is%20u%2Fgrok-1%2C%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20xAI's%20chatbot%2C%20Grok%2C%20according%20to%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20titled%20%26quot%3BFeeling%20the%20Weight%20of%20Endless%20Questions%2C%26quot%3B%20grok-