tle%22%3A%22The%20rush%20for%20Europe's%20%24920%20billion%20warchest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20featuring%20drones%2C%20money%2C%20and%20a%20business%20deal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69456adf04eda4732f2ddb7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKelluu%20began%2C%20as%20startups%20often%20do%2C%20in%20an%20old%20shed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20Finnish%20company%20makes%20airships%20%E2%80%94%20think%20van-sized%20blimps%20%E2%80%94%20originally%20designed%20to%20watch%20over%20power%20lines%20with%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20met%20the%20firm's%20CEO%2C%20Janne%20Hietala%2C%20last%20fall%2C%20he%20arrived%20at%20our%20restaurant%20in%20Joensuu%20with%20news.%20Kelluu%2C%20a%20seven-year-old%20company%2C%20had%20just%20become%20a%20defense%20contractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20NATO%20member%20had%20agreed%20to%20buy%20airships%20for%20surveillance%20under%20an%20alliance%20program%20pushing%20Western%20militaries%20to%20adopt%20new%20tech.%20The%20buyer%20hasn't%20been%20named%2C%20but%20it%20plans%20to%20integrate%20the%20airships%20into%20its%20military%20within%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelluu's%20ascent%20was%20just%20as%20rapid.%20The%20company's%20first%20showcase%20to%20NATO%2C%20Hietala%20said%2C%20was%20in%20November%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelluu%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20big%20in%20a%20market%20that%20hasn't%20been%20kind%20to%20small%20firms.%20Traditionally%2C%20Western%20nations%20have%20depended%20on%20giant%20contractors%20that%20meticulously%20take%20decades%20to%20create%20and%20fine-tune%20systems.%20These%20firms%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bprimes%2C%26quot%3B%20had%20all%20of%20the%20contacts%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20all%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20the%20door%20is%20opening%20for%20founders%20from%20the%20commercial%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvents%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20second%20Trump%20administration%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20drone%20warfare%20%E2%80%94%20have%20jolted%20NATO%20militaries%2C%20who%20now%20fear%20an%20overreliance%20on%20the%20primes.%20European%20generals%20and%20politicians%20alike%20agree%3A%20To%20convince%20Russia%20that%20it%20would%20lose%20a%20war%2C%20the%20continent%20needs%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20ammo%20and%20equipment%20that%20can%20be%20quickly%20designed%2C%20tweaked%2C%20and%20produced%20in%20large%20quantities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20longer%20possible%20to%20just%20adhere%20to%20the%20old%20pace%20of%20months%20and%20years%20of%20planning%2C%20months%20or%20years%20of%20procurement%2C%20months%20or%20years%20of%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Defence%20Innovation%20Accelerator%20for%20the%20North%20Atlantic%2C%20or%20DIANA%2C%20the%20NATO%20agency%20that%20connected%20Kelluu%20with%20alliance%20members%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20conceptualized%20DIANA%20before%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20as%20a%20program%20for%20emerging%20firms%20to%20present%20their%20tech%20to%20allied%20militaries%20and%20potentially%20sign%20contracts.%20Following%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20war%2C%20the%20agency%20was%20established%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20it%20received%204%2C000%20applications%20for%20its%20next%20cohort%2C%20up%20from%202%2C400%20last%20year%20and%201%2C200%20in%20its%20inaugural%20batch%20in%202023.%20At%20least%20half%20of%20these%20firms%20and%20founders%20are%20from%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20who%20once%20viewed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-america-worlds-gun-store-defense-tech-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefense%20sector%20as%20taboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20scouring%20the%20industry.%20According%20to%20the%20NATO%20Innovation%20Fund%20in%20February%2C%20venture%20capital%20investments%20in%20European%20defense%20tech%20reached%20%241%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20up%20by%20four%20times%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20traveled%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202025%20to%20northern%20Europe%2C%20where%20concerns%20about%20war%20with%20Russia%20run%20high%2C%20to%20speak%20with%20defense%20startups%20finding%20their%20corner%20of%20a%20market%20that%20was%20closed%20to%20them%20five%20years%20ago.%20To%20make%20it%20in%20the%20old%20defense%20world%2C%20small%20firms%20typically%20needed%20to%20be%20bought%20by%20a%20prime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20barrier%20fading%2C%20the%20founders%20I%20spoke%20to%20have%20set%20their%20ambitions%20high.%20The%20European%20Union%20has%20a%20new%20goal%20of%20allocating%20%24920%20billion%20more%20to%20defense%20by%202030%2C%20and%20NATO%20members%20are%20raising%20their%20commitment%20to%20spending%205%25%20of%20GDP%20on%20their%20militaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20wonder%20that%20even%20the%20US%20investors%20are%20now%20looking%20at%20the%20European%20landscape%2C%20which%20wasn't%20a%20thing%20a%20year%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Hietala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20this%20collection%20to%20get%20to%20know%20some%20of%20the%20startups%20seeking%20a%20slice%20of%20Europe's%20expanding%20war%20chest%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECredits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Matthew%20Loh%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEditors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sam%20Fellman%2C%20Cheryl%20Teh%2C%20Meghan%20Morris%2C%20Lina%20Batarags%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIllustrator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Tyler%20Le%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-defense-tech-startups-founders-vc-boom-funding-deployment-2026