a%20from%20The%20Numbers%2C%20a%20movie%20financial%20analysis%20website%2C%20shows%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmelania-trump-documentary-surprising-moments-cameos-revelations-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelania%3A%20Twenty%20Days%20to%20History%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20far%20and%20away%20the%20highest-grossing%20documentary%20of%202026%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20%26quot%3BHolding%20Liat%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20documentary%20released%20in%20January%2C%20is%20the%20second%20highest%20earner%20at%20%2428%2C000%20as%20of%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20highest-grossing%20documentaries%20of%202025%20was%20%26quot%3BBecoming%20Led%20Zeppelin%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20earned%20about%20%2410.4%20million%20at%20the%20domestic%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20proves%20that%20an%20original%20idea%20which%20is%20executed%20with%20deliberate%20beauty%20is%20embraced%20by%20fans%20and%20moviegoers%2C%20regardless%20of%20political%20affiliation%2C%26quot%3B%20Marc%20Beckman%2C%20Melania's%20senior%20advisor%20and%20agent%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%2C%20which%20premiered%20on%20January%2030%2C%20offers%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20look%20at%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%202025%20inauguration%20from%20the%20first%20lady's%20perspective.%20Amazon%20MGM%20Studios%20paid%20%2440%20million%20to%20license%20the%20documentary%20and%20an%20additional%20docuseries%20on%20Prime%20Video.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrett-ratner-melania-director-rush-hour-career-timeline-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrett%20Ratner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20known%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BRush%20Hour%26quot%3B%20franchise%20before%20sexual%20misconduct%20allegations%20derailed%20his%20career%20in%202017%2C%20directed%20the%20documentary.%3C%2