before%20we%20could%20cruise%20the%20groomers%20as%20a%20family%2C%20we%20had%20to%20get%20through%20many%20painful%20winters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-differences-skiing-vs-snowboarding-photos-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elearning%20to%20ski%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20could%20teach%20my%20husband.%20The%20problem%20was%20that%20what%20comes%20naturally%20to%20someone%20who's%20been%20doing%20it%20all%20her%20life%20is%20really%20hard%20to%20put%20into%20words%20for%20someone%20who%2C%20well%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20urban%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3c44bb1-762f-4073-91a3-5919913e6ff6%5C%22%3EI%20tried%20teaching%20my%20husband%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20tried!%20We%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-us-ski-team-why-women-tear-the-acls-more-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erented%20skis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hit%20the%20bunny%20hills%2C%20specifically%20at%20a%20small%20Midwest%20ski%20resort%20called%20%26quot%3BAlpine%20Valley.%26quot%3B%20What%20could%20go%20wrong%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20is%20athletic%20and%20approached%20skiing%20with%20the%20confidence%20of%20someone%20who%20is%20good%20at%20every%20sport%20he%20tries.%20Until%20he%20skied.%20As%20we%20crested%20the%20ridge%20of%20the%20first%20hill%2C%20it%20all%20happened%20in%20a%20millisecond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20put%20my%20weak%20%26quot%3Bpizza%20pie!%26quot%3B%20lessons%20into%20action%2C%20he%20immediately%20spun%20wildly%20out%20of%20control%2C%20barreling%20straight%20down%20the%20mountain%2C%20one%20ski%20and%20one%20pole%20in%20the%20air%2C%20screaming%20%26quot%3Bstop%2C%20stop%2C%20stop!%26quot%3B%20until%20he%20eventually%20did%2C%20hitting%20a%20fluorescent%20orange%20snowmaking%20turbine%20with%20such%20force%20that%20it%20slowly%20whirred%20to%20life.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20got%20to%20him%2C%20he%20was%20already%20throwing%20his%20skis%20over